createConnection

public abstract E createConnection(java.lang.String connectionId)

Create a connection of type E to a named resource. The connectionId is an implementation specific id - which in case of RMI backends could be the RMI service address.

If the connection fails it should be retried connectionRetries number of times with a grace time of graceTime seconds in between.

Parameters:
connectionId - opaque implementation specific identifier
Returns:
A connection
